songs.title: Proof
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Baby, what you want, tell me what you want, want
What you want, what you really wanna do
I can take you uptown, take you downtown
Let me know if you really want proof
I'm not the type to just talk it
I strap my boots up and walk it
So baby, let me know if you're ready for school

[Pre-Chorus]
Dancing like you want me
Wouldn't mind it if you tip it
Look what you done started
It's going down tonight

[Chorus]
Now baby, I can't lie
I'm the truth (I'm the truth)
Sign address, get loose
Legs high to the roof (To the roof)
I do my thing, boy, you 'bout to see the proof
I can't lie
I'm the truth (I'm the truth)
Sign address, get loose
Blow your mind to the roof (To the roof)
I do my thing, boy, you 'bout to see the proof

[Post-Chorus]
Ahhhh, shit (Proof, proof, proof, proof, proof)
Ahhhh, shit (See the proof)

[Verse 2]
Baby, I'm a bitch, I'm a real bad bitch
Here I come when you're callin' my name
I can be your fix, let me be your fix boy
Let's go if you wanna play
I'm not the type to just talk it
I strap my boots up and walk it
So baby, let me know if you're ready for school

[Pre-Chorus]
Dancing like you want me
Wouldn't mind it if you tip it
Look what you done started
It's going down tonight

[Chorus]
Now baby, I can't lie
I'm the truth (I'm the truth)
Sign address, get loose
Legs high to the roof (To the roof)
I do my thing, boy, you 'bout to see the proof
I can't lie
I'm the truth (I'm the truth)
Sign address, get loose
Blow your mind to the roof (To the roof)
I do my thing, boy, you 'bout to see the proof

[Post-Chorus]
Ahhhh, shit (Proof, proof, proof, proof, proof)
Ahhhh, shit (See the proof)

[Chorus]
I can't lie
I'm the truth (I'm the truth)
Sign address, get loose
Legs high to the roof (to the roof)
I do my thing, boy, you 'bout to see the proof
I can't lie
I'm the truth (I'm the truth)
Sign address, get loose
Blow your mind to the roof (To the roof)
I do my thing, boy, you 'bout to see the proof (See the proof)

[Outro]
Ba da da da, see the proof
